#: app/templates/landing.html:665
msgid "1. Community Mapping"
msgstr "1. Cartographie communautaire"

#: app/templates/landing.html:667
msgid ""
"Field Tasking Manager empowers communities to map informal settlements, "
"public facilities, and local services for inclusive planning."
msgstr ""
"Le Field Tasking Manager permet aux communautés de cartographier les "
"habitats informels, les équipements publics et les services locaux pour "
"une planification inclusive."

#: app/templates/landing.html:671
msgid "2. Urban Planning and Management"
msgstr "2. Urbanisme et gestion urbaine"

#: app/templates/landing.html:673
msgid ""
"Build smarter cities with coordinated surveys of houses, roads, and "
"utilities through clear, manageable mapping tasks."
msgstr ""
"Construisez des villes plus intelligentes avec des enquêtes coordonnées "
"sur les maisons, les routes et les services publics grâce à des tâches de"
" cartographie claires et gérables."

#: app/templates/landing.html:677
msgid "3. Disaster Response and Recovery"
msgstr "3. Réponse aux catastrophes et reconstruction"

#: app/templates/landing.html:679
msgid ""
"Rapidly map damaged infrastructure after disasters, coordinate "
"volunteers, and deliver reliable data for relief operations."
msgstr ""
"Cartographiez rapidement les infrastructures endommagées après les "
"catastrophes, coordonnez les bénévoles et fournissez des données fiables "
"pour les opérations de secours."

